<br>
go back to mage 101, summoned items:  why do these have to suck?  why cant a mage summon a really useful, if short term weapon?  (short term being the no rent) the only restriction, is that is the mage solos wth it, you have to balance so it doesnt overwrite class deficiancies. (so no snare/root proc , sorry)  that still leaves you with a nice wide window of ideas.  how about an item that procs a form of the old clensing spell (remove 10 pr/dr counters, plus dispell negative effects) or a item that procs a nice mid range damage shield, or a high damage fire DD, etc.  tons of room for options.<br>
<br>
