<br>
     Pretend that your a cleric. In your group you have a cleric (you), a wizard, a monk, a warrior, and a druid. You have one slot left open in your group. you see a Magician LFG, and another class (lets say another warrior). Would you take the Magician, or the warrior? I think it really all comes down to that.<br>
<br>
Sebor Robes<br>
